      "x": 894, "y": 2050, "width": 692, "height": 134,
      "text": "// 模块级 Set，executeTask 入口判断\nconst runningTasks = new Set<string>()\nif (runningTasks.has(taskId)) {\n  log(\"skip: already running\"); return   // 跳过本轮\n}\n// 5 分钟周期 · 单次约 30–60s", "originalText": "// 模块级 Set，executeTask 入口判断\nconst runningTasks = new Set<string>()\nif (runningTasks.has(taskId)) {\n  log(\"skip: already running\"); return   // 跳过本轮\n}\n// 5 分钟周期 · 单次约 30–60s",
